  <lyrics>[V1]
 /Jehová nerqa kachanman, kay tullus kawsanqanku
 Chay kachanri kutícherqa: Qan yachanki, Señorníy./
 //Kay tullus kawsanqanku.// Qan yachanki, Señorníy.
 
[V2]
 /Kay imasta Dios parlarqa; Israel ayllumanta
 Waj suyu jallp’asmantapis kutimpunankumanta/
 /"Espirituyta qojtiy/ samaríy tarinkichej."/
 
</lyrics></song>